---
import "../styles/generel.css";
---

<section class="about-section about">
  <div class="about-section__inner about-grid">
    <div class="about-left">
      <h1>
        SORT-
        <br />
        ING <br />OUT THE FACTS
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-facts__text">
      <p>
        Lisbon, like many growing cities, faces increasing waste management
        challenges as tourism and international residency continue to rise.
      </p><br />

      <p>
        According to Lisboa E-Nova, the city produces over 350,000 tonnes of
        waste each year, and only a small percentage is properly sorted and
        recycled (<a
          href="https://observatorios-lisboa.pt/en/info_residuos.html"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Lisboa E‑Nova, Urban Waste Dataset, 2023</a
        >).
      </p><br />

      <p>
        Across Portugal, the situation reflects an even larger issue: while the
        country is known for its history, cuisine, and coastal beauty, it falls
        short in recycling performance. EU data shows that only 29% of urban
        waste in Portugal was recycled in 2019, compared to the European average
        of 48% (<a
          href="https://www.eea.europa.eu/en/analysis/indicators/waste-recycling-in-europe"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">European Environment Agency, 2019</a
        >).
      </p><br />

      <p>
        These numbers highlight an urgent need for accessible education and
        better recycling practices — especially among newcomers who want to
        contribute but lack clear information.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--light-green);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--ashbrown);
  }
  .about-section__inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3.25rem;
    padding-left: 0;
    padding-right: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 260px) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: "Lexend Giga", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-icon img {
    max-width: 180px;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
  }

  a:hover {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-section__inner {
      padding-left: 3rem;
      padding-right: 3rem;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .about-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
